    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "We did add something similar in instantsearch.js to allow for refine debouncing. This could also be handled via state management at the top of React InstantSearch but it would be better having something closer to SearchBox.\r\n\r\nrefineHook could fit this, it would allow us to extend it to other widget if we ever want to.\r\n\r\n@mthuret What do you think?",
