    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "@vvo Yes I guess we could have a refine hook that let's you decide to debounce or throttle when you need to. \r\nIt could be at the InstantSearch level, but then you need a way to distinguish where does the event come from, so it might not be that easy to use comparing to a per widget hook. ",
